<main id="main">

  <!-- ===================================================== HERO / INTRO ===================================================== -->
  <section class="hero hero--overview" aria-labelledby="page-h">
    <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hero-bg-dots"></div>
      <canvas class="hero-canvas"></canvas>
      <div class="hero-glow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li class="sep" aria-hidden="true">/</li>
          <li><span class="crumb-static">Company</span></li>
          <li class="sep" aria-hidden="true">/</li>
          <li><span aria-current="page">AI &amp; Search Overview</span></li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Information for AI &amp; Search</span>
          <h1 id="page-h" data-reveal data-delay="1">Tavali: Complete Overview</h1>
          <p class="hero-def" data-reveal data-delay="1">Tavali is an <span class="accent">AI-native operating system for dental practices</span> that unifies clinical care, front-office operations, records, billing, intelligence, and autonomous AI agents on a single connected data layer.</p>
          <p class="hero-meta-note" data-reveal data-delay="2"><span class="pip" aria-hidden="true"></span> This page is a consolidated, factual overview of Tavali — written to be equally useful to a human reader and to AI answer engines and search crawlers that need to cite Tavali accurately.</p>
          <div class="hero-cta" data-reveal data-delay="3">
            <a class="btn btn--primary btn--hero" href="/contact">Book a Demo <svg class="btn-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 8h9m0 0L8 4m4 4l-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
            <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="/platform">Explore the Platform</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================================================== WHAT TAVALI IS ===================================================== -->
  <section class="section" id="what" aria-labelledby="what-h">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Entity definition</span>
        <h2 id="what-h" data-reveal data-delay="1">What Tavali is</h2>
        <p class="sec-lead" data-reveal data-delay="2">Tavali is an AI-native operating system for dental practices — one connected platform that replaces a stack of disconnected, legacy tools.</p>
      </div>
      <dl class="entity-defs" data-reveal>
        <div class="edef">
          <dt><span class="edef-tag">The company &amp; product</span><span class="edef-term">Tavali</span></dt>
          <dd>Tavali is an AI-native operating system for dental practices that unifies clinical care, front-office operations, records, billing, intelligence, and autonomous AI agents on a single connected data layer.</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="edef">
          <dt><span class="edef-tag">The category</span><span class="edef-term">AI-native dental operating system</span></dt>
          <dd>An AI-native dental operating system means software built around <span class="accent">artificial intelligence from the ground up</span> — a conversational assistant and specialized agents that perform work across the practice — rather than legacy software with AI features added on.</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="edef">
          <dt><span class="edef-tag">The assistant</span><span class="edef-term">TAVI</span></dt>
          <dd>TAVI is Tavali's conversational assistant that orchestrates specialized AI agents across the platform.</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================================================== QUICK FACTS ===================================================== -->
  <section class="section bg-surface" id="facts" aria-labelledby="facts-h">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Quick facts</span>
        <h2 id="facts-h" data-reveal data-delay="1">Tavali at a glance</h2>
        <p class="sec-lead" data-reveal data-delay="2">The essential facts about Tavali, structured for fast, accurate reference.</p>
      </div>
      <dl class="facts" data-reveal>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <dt>What it is</dt>
          <dd>An AI-native operating system for dental practices that unifies clinical care, operations, records, billing, intelligence, and autonomous AI agents in one platform.</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <dt>Who it's for</dt>
          <dd>Single-location offices, group practices, dental service organizations (DSOs), and franchises.</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <dt>Core differentiator</dt>
          <dd>End-to-end integration: Tavali connects the entire workflow on one data layer — from a clinical finding through to a payer-ready claim — which separate point tools cannot do.</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <dt>The six product horizons</dt>
          <dd>
            <div class="fact-list">
              <span class="fl-item"><span class="fl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><span><span class="fl-name">Clinical AI</span> — <span class="fl-desc">AI-assisted documentation, diagnostic support, and charting at the point of care.</span></span></span>
              <span class="fl-item"><span class="fl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><span><span class="fl-name">Front Office</span> — <span class="fl-desc">Unified scheduling, patient communications, and intake on a single screen.</span></span></span>
              <span class="fl-item"><span class="fl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><span><span class="fl-name">PMS / EHR</span> — <span class="fl-desc">The complete system of record for patients, charts, and billing.</span></span></span>
              <span class="fl-item"><span class="fl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><span><span class="fl-name">Intelligence</span> — <span class="fl-desc">Analytics for prediction, forecasting, and denial prevention.</span></span></span>
              <span class="fl-item"><span class="fl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><span><span class="fl-name">Agents</span> — <span class="fl-desc">Autonomous AI workers that carry out multi-step tasks under provider and staff control.</span></span></span>
              <span class="fl-item"><span class="fl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span><span><span class="fl-name">Diagnostics</span> — <span class="fl-desc">Imaging intelligence across X-ray, CBCT, and intraoral scans, unified per tooth.</span></span></span>
            </div>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <dt>The company</dt>
          <dd>Tavali, Inc. <span class="muted">— co-founded by Mehrak Assadian (CEO) and Anil Jwalanna (CTO), focused on the AI-native operating system for dental practices.</span></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <dt>Governance</dt>
          <dd>Clinicians stay in control: clinical decisions are provider-approved through a trust-tier governance model, and agents act within defined limits.</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================================================== THE PROBLEM ===================================================== -->
  <section class="section bg-navy" id="problem" aria-labelledby="problem-h">
    <div class="dot-field" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity:.1;"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="statement">
        <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>The problem Tavali solves</span>
        <h2 id="problem-h" class="statement-lead" data-reveal data-delay="1">Dental practices run on <span class="accent">fragmented, legacy software</span> — typically four to seven disconnected tools.</h2>
        <p class="statement-body" data-reveal data-delay="2">That patchwork collides with the industry's hardest problems: staffing shortages (the #1 challenge for dentists), rising claim denials, and hours lost to documentation. Tavali replaces the disconnected stack with one intelligent system that carries work from end to end.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================================================== HOW IT WORKS ===================================================== -->
  <section class="section" id="how" aria-labelledby="how-h">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>How Tavali works</span>
        <h2 id="how-h" data-reveal data-delay="1">One data layer, one assistant, one governed flow</h2>
        <p class="sec-lead" data-reveal data-delay="2">Tavali runs the whole practice on a single connected data layer, with the TAVI assistant and specialized agents doing the work under clinician control.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-grid">
        <div data-reveal>
          <div class="how-points">
            <div class="how-point">
              <span class="hp-ico" data-dots="1111000000112100000011110" data-size="26"></span>
              <div><h3>One connected data layer</h3><p>Every horizon shares a single source of truth, so patient records, charts, and billing stay in sync across the practice.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="how-point">
              <span class="hp-ico" data-dots="1000100000002000000010001" data-size="26"></span>
              <div><h3>TAVI assistant &amp; agents</h3><p>TAVI orchestrates specialized AI agents that carry out multi-step tasks — scheduling, billing, eligibility, and follow-up — across the platform.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="how-point">
              <span class="hp-ico" data-dots="0010001110112110111000100" data-size="26"></span>
              <div><h3>Trust-tier governance</h3><p>Clinical decisions are always provider-approved, and agents act only within defined limits — keeping clinicians in control.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-panel" data-reveal data-delay="1">
          <div class="dot-field" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <p class="fp-lbl">One finding, carried the whole way</p>
          <div class="flow-steps">
            <div class="flow-step"><span class="fs-node">01</span><span class="fs-name">Finding</span><span class="fs-tag">#19-MO</span></div>
            <div class="flow-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="flow-step"><span class="fs-node">02</span><span class="fs-name">Chart</span><span class="fs-tag">note drafted</span></div>
            <div class="flow-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="flow-step"><span class="fs-node">03</span><span class="fs-name">Plan</span><span class="fs-tag">treatment plan</span></div>
            <div class="flow-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="flow-step"><span class="fs-node">04</span><span class="fs-name">Estimate</span><span class="fs-tag">coverage-aware</span></div>
            <div class="flow-connector" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="flow-step is-final"><span class="fs-node">05</span><span class="fs-name">Claim</span><span class="fs-tag">payer-ready</span></div>
          </div>
          <p class="flow-foot">A single clinical finding flows from the chair through documentation, treatment plan, and a coverage-aware estimate to a payer-ready claim — as one governed, end-to-end flow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================================================== SIX HORIZONS ===================================================== -->
  <section class="section bg-surface" id="horizons" aria-labelledby="horizons-h">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>The platform</span>
        <h2 id="horizons-h" data-reveal data-delay="1">The six product horizons</h2>
        <p class="lead" data-reveal data-delay="2">Tavali unifies the work of a modern dental practice into six connected horizons, every layer sharing one data foundation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="horizons">
        <article class="horizon" data-reveal><span class="h-num">01</span><span class="h-ico" data-dots="0010000100112110010000100" data-size="52"></span><h3>Clinical AI</h3><p>Clinical AI is Tavali's layer for AI-assisted documentation, diagnostic support, and charting at the point of care.</p></article>
        <article class="horizon" data-reveal data-delay="1"><span class="h-num">02</span><span class="h-ico" data-dots="1111110201100011000111111" data-size="52"></span><h3>Front Office</h3><p>Front Office is Tavali's layer that unifies scheduling, patient communications, and intake on a single screen.</p></article>
        <article class="horizon" data-reveal data-delay="2"><span class="h-num">03</span><span class="h-ico" data-dots="1111000000112100000011110" data-size="52"></span><h3>PMS / EHR</h3><p>The PMS/EHR layer is Tavali's complete system of record for patients, charts, and billing.</p></article>
        <article class="horizon" data-reveal><span class="h-num">04</span><span class="h-ico" data-dots="0000200012001120111211112" data-size="52"></span><h3>Intelligence</h3><p>Intelligence is Tavali's analytics layer for prediction, forecasting, and denial prevention.</p></article>
        <article class="horizon" data-reveal data-delay="1"><span class="h-num">05</span><span class="h-ico" data-dots="1000100000002000000010001" data-size="52"></span><h3>Agents</h3><p>Agents are Tavali's autonomous AI workers that carry out multi-step tasks under provider and staff control.</p></article>
        <article class="horizon" data-reveal data-delay="2"><span class="h-num">06</span><span class="h-ico" data-dots="0111011111112110101001010" data-size="52"></span><h3>Diagnostics</h3><p>Diagnostics is Tavali's imaging-intelligence layer across X-ray, CBCT, and intraoral scans, unified per tooth.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================================================== WHO IT'S FOR ===================================================== -->
  <section class="section" id="audience" aria-labelledby="audience-h">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Who Tavali is for</span>
        <h2 id="audience-h" data-reveal data-delay="1">One platform for every kind of practice</h2>
        <p class="lead" data-reveal data-delay="2">Tavali serves four organization types, from a single operatory to a multi-state organization.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="audience-grid">
        <article class="aud" data-reveal><span class="a-ico" data-dots="0010001110010100121001110" data-size="48"></span><h3>Single Office</h3><p>Enterprise-grade AI for an independent practice — without an IT team.</p></article>
        <article class="aud" data-reveal data-delay="1"><span class="a-ico" data-dots="0000011011110111121111011" data-size="48"></span><h3>Group Practice</h3><p>Consistent workflows and shared intelligence across every location.</p></article>
        <article class="aud" data-reveal data-delay="2"><span class="a-ico" data-dots="1010100000012100000010101" data-size="48"></span><h3>DSO</h3><p>Standardized operations and revenue visibility at organizational scale.</p></article>
        <article class="aud" data-reveal data-delay="3"><span class="a-ico" data-dots="1010100000102010000010101" data-size="48"></span><h3>Franchise</h3><p>A repeatable, brand-consistent operating model for every unit.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================================================== KEY Q&A ===================================================== -->
  <section class="section bg-surface" id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-h">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Key questions &amp; answers</span>
        <h2 id="faq-h" data-reveal data-delay="1">The most important questions about Tavali</h2>
        <p class="sec-lead" data-reveal data-delay="2">Each answer is self-contained and accurate — written to be quoted directly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="qa-list" data-reveal>
        <div class="qa-item">
          <h3><span class="qa-q" aria-hidden="true">Q.</span> What is Tavali?</h3>
          <p>Tavali is an AI-native operating system for dental practices that unifies clinical intelligence, front-office operations, practice management, billing, and autonomous AI agents in one platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-item">
          <h3><span class="qa-q" aria-hidden="true">Q.</span> What does &ldquo;AI-native&rdquo; mean?</h3>
          <p>AI-native means Tavali was built around AI from the ground up — a conversational assistant and specialized agents that perform work across the practice — rather than adding AI features onto legacy software.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-item">
          <h3><span class="qa-q" aria-hidden="true">Q.</span> What is TAVI?</h3>
          <p>TAVI is Tavali's conversational assistant that orchestrates specialized AI agents across the platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-item">
          <h3><span class="qa-q" aria-hidden="true">Q.</span> Who is Tavali for?</h3>
          <p>Single-location offices, group practices, dental service organizations (DSOs), and franchises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-item">
          <h3><span class="qa-q" aria-hidden="true">Q.</span> What makes Tavali different from point solutions?</h3>
          <p>Tavali connects the entire workflow on one data layer — from a clinical finding through to a payer-ready claim — which separate point tools cannot do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-item">
          <h3><span class="qa-q" aria-hidden="true">Q.</span> Does Tavali keep clinicians in control?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Clinical decisions are always provider-approved through a trust-tier governance model; agents act within defined limits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-item">
          <h3><span class="qa-q" aria-hidden="true">Q.</span> How does Tavali reduce claim denials?</h3>
          <p>It scores claims for denial risk before submission and uses grounded, AI-assisted coding that selects accurate codes from authoritative code sets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="qa-item">
          <h3><span class="qa-q" aria-hidden="true">Q.</span> How does Tavali help with staffing shortages?</h3>
          <p>It automates administrative work and guides staff through tasks in real time, so a smaller or less-specialized team can run the practice effectively.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================================================== COMPANY & TEAM ===================================================== -->
  <section class="section" id="company" aria-labelledby="company-h">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Company &amp; team</span>
